《'''离巨星二十英尺'''》（''20 Feet from Stardom''）是一部2013年[[摩根·内维尔|摩根·内维尔]]导演、[[Gil_Friesen|Gil Friesen]]监制的美国音乐题材[[纪录片|纪录片]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Caplan|first=B.|title=Twenty Feet From Stardom Director Morgan Neville on His Own 'Cinderella Moment'|url=http://blogs.miaminewtimes.com/cultist/2013/03/director_morgan_neville_on_pos.php|newspaper=Miami New Times|date=March 13, 2013|accessdate=2014-03-03|archive-date=2013-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224115439/http://blogs.miaminewtimes.com/cultist/2013/03/director_morgan_neville_on_pos.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。讲述几位幕后女声Darlene Love, Merry Clayton, Claudia Lennear, Lisa Fischer, Tata Vega和Judith Hill等伴唱女歌手的故事，他们曾为20世纪最著名的流行歌手们当绿叶，并见证了流行音乐史。<ref>{{cite news |last=Van Syckle|first=Katie|title=Backup Singer Documentary 'Twenty Feet From Stardom' Set for Summer Release |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/backup-singer-documentary-twenty-feet-from-stardom-set-for-summer-release-20130128|newspaper=Rolling Stone|date=January 28, 2013}}</ref>獲選[[第85屆國家評論協會獎|第85屆國家評論協會獎]]五佳紀錄片，並获得[[第86届奥斯卡金像奖|第86届奥斯卡金像奖]]最佳纪录片。

